00:14:41.330 --> 00:14:43.330
to prove that hypothesis.

00:14:43.330 --> 00:14:45.330
We have more trials planned

00:14:45.330 --> 00:14:47.330
for lung cancer,

00:14:47.330 --> 00:14:49.330
pancreatic cancer, ovarian cancer

00:14:49.330 --> 00:14:51.330
and breast cancer.

00:14:51.330 --> 00:14:53.330
And I firmly believe

00:14:53.330 --> 00:14:55.330
that in the next 10 years

00:14:55.330 --> 00:14:57.330
Tumor Treating Fields

00:14:57.330 --> 00:15:00.330
will be a weapon available to doctors and patients

00:15:00.330 --> 00:15:05.330
for all of these most-difficult-to-treat solid tumors.

00:15:06.330 --> 00:15:08.330
I'm also very hopeful

00:15:08.330 --> 00:15:10.330
that in the next decades,

00:15:10.330 --> 00:15:12.330
we will make big strides

00:15:12.330 --> 00:15:15.330
on reducing that death rate

00:15:15.330 --> 00:15:18.330
